# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# __gt__ dict-presence — operator.contains(Cls.__dict__, '__gt__')
#
# asyncio.TimerHandle: TRUE — defines __gt__ as part of the same rich-comparison
#   set. Together with __lt__ and __le__, this gives TimerHandle a complete
#   ordering suitable for use in heapq and sorted containers.
# All other asyncio classes: false — none define __gt__ in their own __dict__.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

